{"word":"G384 - ἀνασκευάζω - anaskeuázō - an-ask-yoo-ad'-zo - Subvert","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀνασκευάζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">anaskeuázō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">an-ask-yoo-ad'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Subvert</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - புரட்டு, வதை, அடி, அமைதியில்லாமல் ஆக்கு"},{"paragraph":"plundering, to overthrow, ravage, destroy"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G303 - ἀνά - aná - an-ah'/303\">G303</a> (in the sense of <i>reversal</i>) and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G4632 - σκεῦος - skeûos - skyoo'-os/4632\">G4632</a>; properly to <i>pack up</i> (baggage), that is, (by implication and figuratively) to <i>upset:</i> - subvert.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}